{"type":"message","id":"6ec6aa89","parentId":"d9d5ea4f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:27.996Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v64av99sxp9w_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n# Session: {date} {time}\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 摘要\n## 主题\n{一句话概括，少于20字}\n\n## AI 决策模式\n{基于 scene/score/strategy 数据分析，1-3句描述}\n\n## 关键决策\n{决策列表，没有则写\"无明确决策\"}\n\n## 重要发现\n{发现列表，没有则写\"无\"}\n\n## 待跟进\n{待办列表，没有则写\"无\"}\n\n<!-- source: {sessionKey} -->\n```\n\n### AI 决策模式分析\n\n摘要 prompt 新增决策模式分析，从 ephemeral 的 v8 决策数据（scene、score、recommendedStrategy、risk factor）提炼：\n- 主要场景类型（clarify/task/troubleshoot/chat/...）\n- 复杂度评分分布\n- 推荐策略分布（DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA）\n- 风险意识表现\n- 互动风格（主动/被动/谨慎/大胆）\n\n## LLM 调用\n\n通过 v8 Router (3102) 调用 LLM 生成摘要，超时 20s。\n\n## Bootstrap 读取\n\nsession 启动时，扫描 `memory/` 下最新摘要文件（按修改时间），读入作为上下文。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776174027983}}
{"type":"message","id":"24e2565e","parentId":"6ec6aa89","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:35.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the architecture better. The session-summary hook generates a summary and stores it in `memory/` directory. The bootstrap hook should read the latest summary from `memory/`. \n\nThe issue might be:\n1. The session-summary hook is writing to `memory/` in the workspace (e.g., `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/`)\n2. But there are two workspace locations: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/` and `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/`\n\nWait, looking at the session-summary hook - it stores files in `memory/` relative to workspace.dir. The workspace is `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/`. So it would be `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/`.\n\n\nBut when I search for session-summary files, I'm only finding them under `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/`, not in the expected location. This suggests either the hook is writing to the wrong workspace directory, or the files are being created in a different place than intended. I should check the handler.js to see where the hook is actually configured to write.","thinkingSignature":"b68ae53b634cba4e2912bafdb871850872b456534bfeb4673f8dcb52b377b678"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rjg2kf99gzl2_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js","limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8659,"output":289,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28698,"cost":{"input":0.0025977,"output":0.00034679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011849999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0041294999999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776174027996,"responseId":"062d76cb0208ff2dd3917bff6e4827de"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd56ef23","parentId":"24e2565e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:35.937Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rjg2kf99gzl2_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * session-summary hook\n *\n * 触发时机: /new 或 /reset\n * 行为: \n *   1. 读取上一个 session 的内容\n *   2. 读取 ephemeral/ 中的记忆碎片\n *   3. 调 LLM 生成结构化摘要 + entity 升格决策\n *   4. 写入 memory/YYYY-MM-DD-summary.md\n *   5. 执行 entity 升格（创建/更新 memory/entities/*.md）\n * 降级: LLM 失败时写规则摘要，不报错\n */\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport os from \"node:os\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\n\n// ─── Constants ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nconst MEMORY_DIR = path.join(\n  process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR ||\n    path.join(os.homedir(), \".openclaw\", \"workspace\"),\n  \"memory\"\n);\nconst EPHEMERAL_DIR = path.join(MEMORY_DIR, \"ephemeral\");\nconst ENTITIES_DIR = path.join(MEMORY_DIR, \"entities\");\nconst LLM_TIMEOUT_MS = 20_000;\n\n// ─── Types (JSDoc) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n/**\n * @typedef {Object} SessionEntry\n * @property {string} [sessionFile]\n * @property {string} [sessionId]\n */\n\n/**\n * @typedef {Object} HookContext\n * @property {SessionEntry} [previousSessionEntry]\n * @property {SessionEntry} [sessionEntry]\n */\n\n/**\n * @typedef {Object} EphemeralEntry\n * @property {string} timestamp\n * @property {string} sessionKey\n * @property {string} text\n * @property {string} textPreview\n * @property {object} classification\n * @property {object} scoring\n */\n\n// ─── Session File Resolution ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n/**\n * 从 context 中提取 session 文件路径。\n * 优先使用 previousSessionEntry（旧 session，即刚结束的那个）。\n * @param {HookContext} context\n  * @returns {string|Promise<string|null>}\n */\nfunction resolveSessionFile(context, workspaceDir) {\n  const prev = context?.previousSessionEntry;\n  if (prev?.sessionFile) return prev.sessionFile;\n\n  const curr = context?.sessionEntry;\n  if (curr?.sessionFile) return curr.sessionFile;\n\n  // Webchat sessions have no .jsonl files — search sessions directory\n  // 实际 session 数据在 agents/main/sessions/，不是 sessions/\n  let sessionsDir;\n  if (workspaceDir) {\n    sessionsDir = path.join(workspaceDir, 'agents', 'main', 'sessions');\n  } else {\n    sessionsDir = path.join(os.homedir(), '.openclaw', 'agents', 'main', 'sessions');\n  }\n  const sessionId = prev?.sessionId || curr?.sessionId;\n  return findPreviousSessionFile(prev?.sessionFile || curr?.sessionFile, sessionId, sessionsDir);\n}\n\n\n[600 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776174035926}}
{"type":"message","id":"6558e053","parentId":"fd56ef23","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:43.141Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the session-summary hook writes to `memory/` directory. But looking at the code, `MEMORY_DIR` is set to `path.join(process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR || path.join(os.homedir(), \".openclaw\", \"workspace\"), \"memory\")`.\n\nThe `OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR` is `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/` (based on the workspace being `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main`). So the memory directory would be `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/`.\n\n\nBut when I check the actual session-summary files, they're appearing in `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/` instead, which suggests either the environment variable isn't being set correctly or the hook is using a different code path. I need to look at how bootstrap hook reads these files to understand the disconnect.","thinkingSignature":"86104c041e78222e50b80253cb782924a94027458b5739c173afc684164d109e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_buzswmow1ey1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks -name \"*.js\" | xargs grep -l \"session-summary\\|bootstrapFiles\\|summary\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9609,"output":245,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29604,"cost":{"input":0.0028826999999999998,"output":0.000294,"cacheRead":0.0011849999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0043617}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776174035937,"responseId":"062d76d36ff4da898a7841b27c158998"}}
