{"type":"message","id":"49ae2f58","parentId":"3c454ba4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:45.387Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5subikpxguiy_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"6: * 2. Previous session's summary (memory/*-session-summary.md) as bootstrap context\n34: * Find and read the most recent session-summary file.\n35: * Looks in memory/ for *-session-summary.md files, returns most recent by mtime.\n45:    const summaryFiles = files.filter(f => f.endsWith('-session-summary.md'));\n47:    if (summaryFiles.length === 0) return null;\n51:      summaryFiles.map(async (f) => ({\n61:    // Strip <!-- summary-only --> and <!-- source: ... --> tags for clean injection\n63:      .replace(/<!-- summary-only -->/g, '')\n97:  if (!Array.isArray(event.context.bootstrapFiles)) {\n102:  event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n108:  // 2. Inject previous session summary (memory chain key step)\n109:  const summary = await getLatestSessionSummary();\n110:  if (summary) {\n111:    event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n113:      content: summary,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"6: * 2. Previous session's summary (memory/*-session-summary.md) as bootstrap context\n34: * Find and read the most recent session-summary file.\n35: * Looks in memory/ for *-session-summary.md files, returns most recent by mtime.\n45:    const summaryFiles = files.filter(f => f.endsWith('-session-summary.md'));\n47:    if (summaryFiles.length === 0) return null;\n51:      summaryFiles.map(async (f) => ({\n61:    // Strip <!-- summary-only --> and <!-- source: ... --> tags for clean injection\n63:      .replace(/<!-- summary-only -->/g, '')\n97:  if (!Array.isArray(event.context.bootstrapFiles)) {\n102:  event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n108:  // 2. Inject previous session summary (memory chain key step)\n109:  const summary = await getLatestSessionSummary();\n110:  if (summary) {\n111:    event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n113:      content: summary,","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776174045377}}
{"type":"message","id":"21a7b89d","parentId":"49ae2f58","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:53.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the bootstrap hook reads session-summary files from `memory/` directory. But the files are named `*-session-summary.md` (based on the grep). Let me check what the actual naming convention is and where files are being written.\n\nFrom the hook.js I read earlier, the file format is `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md` with `<!-- summary-only -->` marker. But the bootstrap hook looks for `*-session-summary.md` files.\n\nThis might be a naming mismatch! The session-summary hook writes files like `2026-04-14-无会话内容.md` but the bootstrap hook looks for `*-session-summary.md`.\n \nLooking at the actual files on disk, I found `2026-04-13-session-summary.md` in the memory directory, but when I checked the session-summary handler's write logic around line 240, it constructs the filename as `YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md` rather than including \"session-summary\" in the name. So either the naming convention changed at some point, or there's a discrepancy between what the hook is supposed to do and what it's actually doing.","thinkingSignature":"2ab3b96e602fd57f466826bfa3aca19871ba4042a04e6dbf718417e560b3a0e6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i2eyj67i63sw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js","offset":220,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10196,"output":290,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30236,"cost":{"input":0.0030588,"output":0.000348,"cacheRead":0.0011849999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0045918}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776174045388,"responseId":"062d76dc6ddf70e834be200c154ff39f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"aee17acc","parentId":"21a7b89d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:40:53.768Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i2eyj67i63sw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  /** @type {EphemeralEntry[]} */\n  const allEntries = [];\n  \n  try {\n    const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10); // YYYY-MM-DD\n    const files = await fs.promises.readdir(EPHEMERAL_DIR);\n    \n    for (const file of files) {\n      if (!file.endsWith('.jsonl') || !file.startsWith(today)) continue;\n      const filePath = path.join(EPHEMERAL_DIR, file);\n      try {\n        const content = await fs.promises.readFile(filePath, 'utf-8');\n        const lines = content.trim().split('\\n');\n        for (const line of lines) {\n          if (!line.trim()) continue;\n          try {\n            const entry = JSON.parse(line);\n            if (entry.sessionKey === sessionKey) {\n              allEntries.push(entry);\n            }\n          } catch { /* skip */ }\n        }\n      } catch { /* skip file errors */ }\n    }\n  } catch { /* ephemeral dir may not exist */ }\n  \n  // 去重（相同 text 的条目只保留最新）\n  const seen = new Set();\n  const uniqueEntries = allEntries.filter(e => {\n    const key = e.text.slice(0, 100);\n    if (seen.has(key)) return false;\n    seen.add(key);\n    return true;\n  });\n  \n  // 限制最多 20 条，防止 token 爆炸\n  const entries = uniqueEntries.slice(-20);\n  \n  // 生成预览文本\n  const preview = entries.length > 0\n    ? entries.map(e => `[${e.classification?.scene || '?'}] score=${e.scoring?.score || 0} \"${e.textPreview || e.text.slice(0, 80)}\"`).join('\\n')\n    : '';\n  \n  return { entries, preview };\n}\n\n// ─── LLM Generation ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n/**\n * @param {string} sessionContent\n * @param {string} ephemeralPreview\n * @returns {string}\n */\nfunction buildSummaryPrompt(sessionContent, ephemeralPreview) {\n  return `你是一个会话摘要生成器，同时负责记忆升格决策。\n\n给定以下对话记录和实时捕获的记忆碎片，生成：\n1. 一个结构化摘要\n2. 需要升格为 entity 页的记忆条目（只有真正重要的、涉及系统/项目/偏好的才升格）\n\n## 对话记录：\n${sessionContent || \"(无会话内容)\"}\n\n## 记忆碎片（来自 ephemeral/，包含 v8 决策数据）：\n${ephemeralPreview || \"(无碎片)\"}\n\n## AI 决策模式分析（从碎片中的 classification/scoring 数据提炼）：\n基于上述记忆碎片中的 scene（场景）、score（复杂度评分）、recommendedStrategy（推荐策略）数据，分析本 session 的 AI 决策模式：\n- 主要场景类型是什么？（task/clarify/troubleshoot/chat/...）\n- 复杂度评分分布如何？（低分=简单指令，高分=多步骤任务）\n- 推荐策略分布？（DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA）\n- 风险意识表现如何？（risk factor 是否有异常高值）\n- 与用户互动的整体风格？（主动/被动/谨慎/大胆）\n\n要求：\n- 主题：一句话概括，少于20字\n- 关键决策：列出所有决策，没有则写\"无明确决策\"\n- 重要发现：列出有价值的结论/教训，没有则写\"无\"\n- 待跟进：列出未完成事项，没有则写\"无\"\n- AI 决策模式：基于上述分析给出简短描述（1-3句）\n\n[381 more lines in file. Use offset=300 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776174053758}}
