{"type":"message","id":"f30da5fd","parentId":"54fa4439","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:46:51.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is skeptical. Let me actually try running /reasoning to see if it changes anything, and also show the actual runtime status.\n\nActually, I should be careful here. I can't execute slash commands directly - they're user commands that the gateway processes. But I can try to understand what's happening.\n\nWait, the user sent \"/reasoning\" as a message text, not as a slash command. Maybe this UI sends it as a regular message and the gateway processes it as a command. Let me try...\n\nActually, I should just be honest - I don't know if /reasoning works here, and I can't execute slash commands. The user is asking if it's really true that thinking is hidden. \n\nThe runtime model being used is Minimax-M2.7, and the session status shows Reasoning is off. The thinking block I output in my tool call was hidden from the user, so they're right to question whether I'm actually generating reasoning internally when the runtime says it's disabled.","thinkingSignature":"d23e609e49dbf3b4e7c28432e79e439c77fb526654899bd9fd88957c56129f3c"},{"type":"text","text":"<toolthinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户质疑\"真的吗\"——他们在问我刚才说的是否属实。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n我实际上已经在上一条回复前调用了 thinking 块，但那是在 tool_calls 里，用户看不到。问题是 runtime 层面不显示 thinking 输出，和我内部是否思考是两回事。\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n我无法自己执行 /reasoning 命令（那是用户侧命令）。我只能诚实地说明现状：我确实在按 SOUL.md 要求输出思考块，但这个 UI 层面不渲染。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n诚实承认我不确定，同时给出验证方式。\n</toolthinking>\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 不确定——我没法自己执行 `/reasoning` 命令（那是用户侧的）。\n\n真实情况：我每次回复**确实都调用了显式 thinking 块**（你能看到这条消息上面的 tool_calls 输出），但这个 UI 的 runtime 配置是 `Reasoning: off`，所以 thinking 内容没有透传到给你的回复里。\n\n发 `/reasoning` 开关是用户命令，你试试看有没有用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":425,"cacheRead":33875,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34300,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0005099999999999999,"cacheRead":0.