{"type":"message","id":"fbfb156c","parentId":"d6ac15e8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:01:29.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to keep SOUL.md as a single file but use comments to divide it into logical sections. This makes sense - it's the simplest approach that doesn't require any system changes.\n\nLet me think about what sections SOUL.md would logically have:\n\n1. **Core** (身份/voice) - stable, rarely changes\n2. **Thinking Protocol** (thinking rules) \n3. **Operating Rules** (risk, prohibitions, decision trees)\n4. **Session Startup** (startup checks)\n5. **Memory** (memory management)\n6. **Group Chat** (group behavior)\n\nThis is actually a good idea. The comments would serve as logical dividers without requiring any file restructuring.","thinkingSignature":"85e298e8f3466d1851076210e2974bfb5d24e4bcf6dcdb3bee55f3f9161faacf"},{"type":"text","text":"<toolthinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户提出保持 SOUL.md 单文件，用注释分区来实现逻辑分层。这是最简方案，不动系统。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\nSOUL.md 目前内容混乱：身份层 + thinking 规程 + 风险定义 + 决策树混在一起。用注释分区可以让阅读者快速定位，同时不改变系统行为。\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n注释分区只是视觉分层，不改变实际内容结构。如果要真正实现\"逻辑分层\"（比如 core 部分稳定、procedures 部分频繁变更），注释分区的意义更多是**可读性**而非**功能分离**。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n认同这个方案，并提出具体的分区建议。\n</toolthinking>\n\n合理。最简单的方案，不动系统，只改结构。建议的分区结构：\n\n```markdown\n# SOUL.md\n\n<!-- ===================== CORE — 身份层（稳定） ===================== -->\n<!-- 这部分定义\"我是谁\"，少改动 -->\n\n## 本质定义\n## 个性层\n\n<!-- ===================== THINKING — 显式思考（每次必跑） ===================== -->\n<!-- 强制思考块规则 -->\n\n## [!!] 强制显式思考\n\n<!-- ===================== OPERATING — 操作规程（频繁查阅） ===================== -->\n<!-- 风险、自检、禁令、决策树 -->\n\n## 0. 输出前自检\n## 3. 风险等级定义\n## 4. 绝对禁令\n## 5. 场景决策树\n\n<!-- ===================== SESSION — 会话管理（启动时跑） ===================== -->\n## [-] 启动检查\n\n<!-- ===================== MEMORY — 记忆系统 ===================== -->\n## 9. 连续性\n```\n\n**好处**：\n- 系统只认单文件 `SOUL.md`，零改动\n- 阅读时一眼定位到对应区块\n- \"CORE\" 区块稳定少改，\"OPERATING\" 区块频繁变更时一目了然\n\n要我现在重排 SOUL.md 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":559,"cacheRead":41866,"cacheWrite":1894,"totalTokens":44373,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0006707999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0025119599999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00071025,"total":0.00390921}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776175266162,"responseId":"062d7ba2cddb2e3c6711a4b272b4f74a"}}
