{"type":"message","id":"3751ee0f","parentId":"680efbb8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:19:09.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the framework is fully operational/working. Based on what we know from the session history:\n\n1. 3103 scorer - ✅ online\n2. 3105 classifier v2 - ✅ online\n3. session-summary hook - ✅ writes files (but had a filename bug, fixed)\n4. bootstrap hook - ✅ logic correct (but needed the filename fix in session-summary to work)\n5. ephemeral - ✅ capturing data\n\nThe memory chain:\n- ephemeral → session-summary: ✅ (hook works, file naming bug fixed)\n- session-summary → bootstrap: ✅ (now that filename format is fixed)\n- bootstrap → LLM: ✅ (logic verified)\n\n\n- \nSo the core components are functioning end-to-end now that the filename format issue has been resolved. The main thing to watch for is whether this actually holds up when we trigger a fresh /new session and the bootstrap hook reads from the corrected session-summary files.","thinkingSignature":"8673a88ecb5189cbd2b40c2c76a99f2e9cbee465aabc8e7f7a65548ae249ad4a"},{"type":"text","text":"核心组件都在线，但链路今天才修好，还没端到端验证过。\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 3103 Scorer | ✅ 在线 |\n| 3105 Classifier v2 | ✅ 在线 |\n| ephemeral 捕获 | ✅ 正常 |\n| session-summary hook 写文件 | ✅ 正常（文件名 bug 已修） |\n| bootstrap hook 读文件 | ✅ 逻辑正确（依赖文件名修复） |\n| bootstrap → LLM 实际注入 | ❓ 还未 /new 验证 |\n\n最后一步还没真实跑通——需要一次真正的 `/new` 让整个链路闭合。要现在试一次吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":329,"cacheRead":57977,"cacheWrite":1200,"totalTokens":59560,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0003948,"cacheRead":0.0034786199999999995,"cacheWrite":0.00045,"total":0.00433962}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776176332291,"responseId":"062d7fcb5c106a04fc0e63713d465332"}}
